vote.title: A resolution naming the 3 Sisters Lakes: Comanche Nahmi Lake, Wichita ita:iʔh Lake, and Lipan Apache Mbátí Lake (Each lake name includes the Native word for "sister" specific to that tribe: Comanche - Nahmi, Wichita - ita:iʔh, Lipan Apache - Mbátí) located in the Dallas Floodway Levee System near Westmoreland Road - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
